@host = http://localhost:3000

### Health check
GET {{host}}/health


# CARDAPIO

### Criar item (captura o id em @itemId)
# @name criarItem
POST {{host}}/menu-items
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "X-Burger",
  "price": 25.5
}

###
@itemId = {{criarItem.response.body.id}}

### Criar item indisponivel 

POST {{host}}/menu-items
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Milkshake",
  "price": 15,
  "available": false
}

### Listar itens
GET {{host}}/menu-items

### Detalhar item
GET {{host}}/menu-items/{{itemId}}

### Atualizar item (preco / disponibilidade)
PATCH {{host}}/menu-items/{{itemId}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "price": 27.9,
  "available": true
}

### Remover item
# DELETE {{host}}/menu-items/{{itemId}}


# PEDIDOS  


### Criar pedido (captura o id em @orderId)
# @name criarPedido
POST {{host}}/orders
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "table": 5,
  "items": [
    { "menuItemId": "{{itemId}}", "quantity": 2 }
  ]
}

###
@orderId = {{criarPedido.response.body.id}}

### Listar pedidos
GET {{host}}/orders

### Detalhar pedido (veja o status mudar ao longo do fluxo)
GET {{host}}/orders/{{orderId}}

### Cancelar pedido (bloqueado com 409 se ja estiver IN_KITCHEN)
PATCH {{host}}/orders/{{orderId}}/cancel


# PAGAMENTO  


### Pagar pedido
POST {{host}}/payments
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "orderId": "{{orderId}}"
}

### Consultar status do pagamento
GET {{host}}/payments/{{orderId}}



# NOTIFICACAO


### Listar notificacoes enviadas a cozinha
GET {{host}}/notifications



# CASOS DE ERRO (validacao / acoplamento com o cardapio)


### Pedido com item inexistente -> 400
POST {{host}}/orders
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "table": 1,
  "items": [
    { "menuItemId": "00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000", "quantity": 1 }
  ]
}

### Pedido sem quantity -> 400
POST {{host}}/orders
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "table": 1,
  "items": [
    { "menuItemId": "{{itemId}}" }
  ]
}
